# OBJECT::DOOR_SYSTEM_SET_HOLD_OPEN

## Summary
Set the door to hold open

## Parameters
* **INT** doorEnumHash
* **BOOL** holdOpen

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Includes networking check: ownership vs. or the door itself **isn't** networked.
